EnExplanation: The past participle form of the verb 'töötama', meaning to have done work or to have been employed.

Samples.EeSentence: Ta on palju töötanud selle projekti kallal.
Samples.EnSentence: He has worked a lot on this project.

Samples.EeSentence: Ma olen töötanud siin juba kaks aastat.
Samples.EnSentence: I have worked here for two years.
